<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="10">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block">知乎用户、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$zhang-shuai-19-68" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/zhang-shuai-19-68" class="zg-link" title="张帅">张帅</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$da-shu-you-ji-rou-76" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/da-shu-you-ji-rou-76" class="zg-link" title="大叔有肌肉">大叔有肌肉</a></span>
